EASTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
GABON.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 22 MAR
   BY M/V BGP EXPLORER TOWING THREE FOUR MILE
   LONG CABLES IN AREA BOUND BY
   01-38.3S 008-59.9E, 02-09.1S 009-19.5E,
   02-06.1S 009-24.2E, 01-35.3S 009-04.6E.
   FIVE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 23 MAR 14.
